        "rt_tldr": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li><strong>What it is:</strong> Supplements people use to support focus, memory, mood, or energy.</li><li><strong>Who it's for:</strong> Beginners who want simple, safe-minded starts — no complex stacks required.</li><li><strong>How to start:</strong> Use 3 steps — Base → Choline support → Goal-specific booster.</li></ul>",
            "sensitivity": "none"
          }
        },
        "pt_quick": {
          "type": "pro_tip",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Pro Tip",
            "content": "<p>If you're in a rush, jump to the <strong>3-Step Quick-Start</strong> section for a build-your-stack walkthrough in under 60 seconds.</p>",
            "icon": "lightbulb"
          }
        },
        "h_what": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "What are nootropics?",
            "level": "h2",
            "anchor_id": "what-are-nootropics"
          }
        },
        "rt_what": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Nootropics are substances — often dietary supplements — that people use to support mental performance such as focus, memory, motivation, or stress resilience. They are not magic, and effects vary. They work best alongside good sleep, nutrition, and movement.</p><ul><li>May support attention, learning, clarity, or stress balance.</li><li>Not medical treatment. Consult your clinician if you have a condition or take meds.</li><li>Start low, add slowly; some items require cycling.</li></ul>",
            "sensitivity": "none"
          }
        },
        "h_choose": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "How to choose",
            "level": "h2",
            "anchor_id": "how-to-choose"
          }
        },
        "rt_choose": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ol><li>Pick your primary goal (Focus, Calm, Memory, Energy)</li><li>Choose caffeine-friendly or caffeine-free</li><li>Note sensitivities (stimulants, sleep)</li></ol>",
            "sensitivity": "none"
          }
        },
        "pt_choose": {
          "type": "pro_tip",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Warning",
            "content": "<p>Some compounds (e.g., Phenylpiracetam, Phenibut) are <strong>not</strong> beginner daily tools. Understand risks and consult a clinician first.</p>",
            "icon": "warning"
          }
        },
        "h_quick": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The 3-Step Quick-Start",
            "level": "h2",
            "anchor_id": "quick-start"
          }
        },
        "h_step1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "1) Choose your Base",
            "level": "h3",
            "anchor_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rt_step1": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li><strong>Caffeine + L-Theanine</strong> — smooth focus for task sprints.</li><li><strong>Lion's Mane</strong> — caffeine-free clarity; long-game support.</li><li><strong>L-Theanine (solo)</strong> — calm clarity; pairs with coffee or tea.</li></ul>",
            "sensitivity": "caffeine"
          }
        },
        "h_step2": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "2) Add a Choline Source",
            "level": "h3",
            "anchor_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rt_step2": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Alpha-GPC or CDP-Choline; pick one. Both provide the acetylcholine precursor your brain needs for focus and memory — doubling up is unnecessary.</p>",
            "sensitivity": "none"
          }
        },
        "h_step3": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "3) Layer a Goal-Booster",
            "level": "h3",
            "anchor_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rt_step3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li><strong>Bacopa Monnieri</strong> — memory and calm; consistent use over weeks.</li><li><strong>Rhodiola Rosea</strong> — resilience on stressful days.</li><li><strong>Noopept</strong> — occasional situational clarity.</li></ul>",
            "sensitivity": "none"
          }
        },
        "pt_step3": {
          "type": "pro_tip",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Pro Tip",
            "content": "<p>If your base already includes a choline source (e.g., Alpha-GPC in a pre-made stack), skip Step 2 — no need to double up.</p>",
            "icon": "info"
          }
        },
        "h_safety": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Safety, tolerance & expectations",
            "level": "h2",
            "anchor_id": "safety"
          }
        },
        "rt_safety": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Start low; one change at a time.</li><li>Journal your response (focus, mood, sleep, timing).</li><li>Cycle as needed — 4-6 weeks on, 1 week off is a common rhythm.</li><li>Mind interactions; talk to a clinician if unsure.</li></ul>",
            "sensitivity": "none"
          }
        },
        "rt_safety_caff": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>Caffeine note:</strong> If you're caffeine-sensitive, Lion's Mane, Theanine, Bacopa, and Ashwagandha enable fully caffeine-free stacks with zero stimulant load.</p>",
            "sensitivity": "caffeine"
          }
        },
        "rt_safety_sleep": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>Sleep note:</strong> Take stimulating compounds (Caffeine + NALT, Phenylpiracetam) before 2 PM. Theanine and Ashwagandha are safe closer to evening.</p>",
            "sensitivity": "sleep"
          }
        },
        "rt_safety_gi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>GI note:</strong> Bacopa and high-dose Alpha-GPC can cause mild GI discomfort in some users. Take with a meal containing healthy fats for better absorption and fewer side effects.</p>",
            "sensitivity": "gi"
          }
        },
        "rt_safety_anxiety": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>Anxiety note:</strong> If anxiety-prone, avoid Phenibut and high-dose caffeine. L-Theanine and Ashwagandha KSM-66 are calming choices.</p>",
            "sensitivity": "anxiety"
          }
        },
        "h_real": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Real-world use",
            "level": "h2",
            "anchor_id": "real-world-use"
          }
        },
        "rt_real": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Nootropics fit real routines. Here are three common setups our customers use:</p><ul><li><strong>Deep-work morning:</strong> Coffee + Theanine, CDP-Choline, 90-min focus block.</li><li><strong>Evening study:</strong> Lion's Mane AM; Theanine PM; Bacopa with dinner.</li><li><strong>Presentation day:</strong> Caffeine + NALT + Theanine pre-meeting; CDP earlier.</li></ul>",
            "sensitivity": "none"
          }
        },
        "bq_real_1": {
